The paper deals with visual attention and image classification, which are core topics in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of a novel attention mechanism and reinforcement learning also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves the use of natural language processing techniques for multi-label classification (cs.CL). Finally, the paper's use of neural networks and deep learning techniques suggests a possible fit with the neural and evolutionary computing subcategory (cs.NE).
